Column 1 — BU (Lookup → Business Unit)

Display name: BU
Description: The Business Unit this match token belongs to. When Flow 1 finds this token in a LeanIX Org Unit path, it resolves the application to this BU.
Data type: Lookup
Related table: Business Unit
Required: Required (this token is meaningless without a BU)
Advanced:

Schema name: bu
Audit: ON



Column 2 — Priority (Integer)

Display name: Priority
Description: Higher priority wins when multiple BU tokens match the same Org Unit path. Use only when longest-match-wins doesn't reflect business intent. Default 0.
Data type: Whole number
Required: Optional
Default value: 0
Advanced:

Schema name: priority
Audit: ON



Column 3 — Active (Yes/No)

Display name: Active
Description: When Yes, Flow 1 considers this token during BU resolution. When No, the token is ignored. Use to deactivate without deleting (preserves audit history).
Data type: Yes/No
Required: Optional
Default value: Yes
Advanced:

Schema name: active
Audit: ON
